* Desmonus growled as she noticed their looks.*

" And enough with the hostile looks, please. Beating eachother to a pulp 
won't get me in your beds any easier then it is now..."

* There, it was now out in the open, letting them know that she caught on to 
what they were trying to do.*

* She then walked ahead a bit and turned her head to look at them.*

" Besides, we can all share..."

* She then gave them a little wink before looking straight ahead again, 
continuing on her way.
If she had to she would make love to both of them to simply just to shut 
them both up, but probably then the situation would probably be the same.
But she was rather hungry, perhaps later she would feed on one of them, or 
both.*
